dataset_id: BOREAS SERM Forest Cover Data of Saskatchewan in Vector Format
title: BOREAS SERM Forest Cover Data of Saskatchewan in Vector Format
summary: A condensed forest cover type digital map of Saskatchewan and is a product of the Saskatchewan Environment and Resource Management, Forestry Branch-Inventory Unit (SERM-FBIU).  Map was generalized from SERM township maps of vegetation cover at an approximate scale of 1:63,000 (1 in. = 1 mile).  The cover information was iteratively generalized until it was compiled on a 1:1,000,000 scale map base.
